page.title: 16Hobbies of a boy and a girl
page.content: { KEYRINGS}I have a collection of keyrings.The proper name is keyrings but some people call them key fobs.I get them from places that I have visited_mainly from France.I like my keyrings.I make a cardboard cut out of a key and write on it where and when I got the keyring.I have some shelves next to my bed.There are some supports to hold the shelves up,with some holes in.There I hang up the wire with the keyrings on.When I get more keyrings I put them on other holes.I have been collecting for a year.I have 345. John Bodkin{ {CAR REGISTRATION NUMBERS}I like collecting these.It is something to do.I keep car numbers so that when I am older and have children I will give them to my eldest child and hope they will get more numbers.I have over 500 numbers. Rebecca Stevenson
